<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_288" id="143v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_288_r1l1">Ludwig vnd <expan>Frıdr<ex>ich</ex></expan> Grafen cʒü <expan>Ötinge<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_288_r1l2"><expan>Gnedıge<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſchrıb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt vmb <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> VVirıchen von </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_288_r1l3"> <expan>Trewtling<ex>en</ex></expan> / <expan>Laſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnad <expan>wıſſe<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ der 
<del rend="strikethrough">cʒü </del> nicht anheim </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_288_r1l4">ıſt / vnd ſo bedürffen wir ſein auch 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>ſelb<ex>er</ex></expan></del> von vnſerſelbs <expan>nötlıch<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_288_r1l5"><expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> / daʒ wir ſein auf die cʒeit nicht geraten <expan>müge<ex>n</ex></expan> / vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_288_r1l6"><expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wol / daʒ Jr vns das nicht für v̈bel habt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_288_r1l7">wan vvo wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lıeb vnd dienſte <expan>beweıſe<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>möcht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_288_r1l8">Das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir allcʒeıt <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>Sabb<ex>at</ex>o</expan> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> <expan>Pet<ex>ri</ex></expan> et Paulȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_288" id="143v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Ludwig und <expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, grafen czü
                                <expan>Ötinge<ex>n</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Gnedige<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, als ir uns
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> habt umb
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>n</expan> Wirichen von
                                <expan>Trewtling<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan>
                        wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex></expan> gnad <expan>wisse<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz der
                        nicht anheim ist, und so bedürffen wir sein auch von unserselbs
                                <expan>nötlich<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz wir sein auf die czeit nicht geraten
                                <expan>müge<ex>n</ex></expan>, und <expan>getrawe<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wol, daz ir uns das nicht für übel habt. Wan
                        wo wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lieb und dienste
                            <expan>beweise<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>möcht<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        allczeit <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sabb<ex>at</ex>o</expan>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan>
<expan>Pet<ex>ri</ex></expan> et Pauli.</ab>
</div>
